snippet.title: Gigantosaurus The Game | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch out! Gigantosaurus The Game is coming on March 27th! Explore and race around the world of Gigantosaurus and help Tiny, Mazu, Bill and Rocky save their world!

Available to pre-order now 👉 www.outrightgames.com/gigantosaurus
